{"tid":1842764,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"防病毒社區爆發 海洋公園今起暫停開放 直至另行通告","createTime":"2020-01-26T01:39:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-26T01:45:15.000Z","uid":42804,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"0332ba3adb1cc35f1dc0291bbd5d04315d0340a7","tid":1842764,"uid":42804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T01:39:33.000Z","msg":"海洋公園宣佈，鑑於政府已把武漢肺炎的應變級別提升至「緊急」級別， 考慮到訪客及員工安全，海洋公園將於今天起暫停開放，直至另行通告。公園將緊密監察事件發展，並配合政府的防疫工作及預防疾病在社區爆發之措施。 <br />\n<br />\n如訪客持有於公園售票處或官方網站購買之受影響日期標準門票、晚間入場門票/套票、學生門票或動物活動門票，請保留門票，作為日後由公園直接換票或退款之用。經由公園正式授權旅行社或售票平台購入之受影響門票，公園將協助提供相關換票或退票資料。不便之處，敬請原諒。<br />\n<br />\n有關公園重新開放日期，以及換票及退票細則，<a href=\"http://將稍後於海洋公園官方網站www.oceanpark.com.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E5%B0%87%E7%A8%8D%E5%BE%8C%E6%96%BC%E6%B5%B7%E6%B4%8B%E5%85%AC%E5%9C%92%E5%AE%98%E6%96%B9%E7%B6%B2%E7%AB%99www.oceanpark.com.hk&d=DF3UGDbnXTwcWfCLvBafJbXdyKWV89KwSxbYnQ5zRIM%3D&h=57e9a57f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">將稍後於海洋公園官方網站www.oceanpark.com.hk</a>公佈。<br />\n【武漢肺炎】防病毒社區爆發 海洋公園今起暫停開放 直至另行通告<br />\n <a href=\"https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20200126&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=60525767\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20200126%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D60525767&d=DF3UGDbnXTwcWfCLvBafJbXdyKWV89KwSxbYnQ5zRIM%3D&h=d0fc8f58\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20200126%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D60525767&h=9af5bc25\" target=\"_blank\">https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20200126&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=60525767</a>"},{"pid":"43139463986678a610cea1cd399a192bbd979d5f","tid":1842764,"uid":66719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T01:43:17.000Z","msg":"都好，唔開蝕少d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75d708e64c1baf6534cd2c8f62e0c5e0c2038ce4","tid":1842764,"uid":3786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-26T01: